text:
Alex Rodriguez is giving his girl a tour of his old stomping ground!

The former baseball pro visited New York's Yankee Stadium with his girlfriend, Jennifer Lopez, on Friday.

RELATED: Jennifer Lopez and Alex Rodriguez Step Out in Summer Chic Styles for Another Dinner Date in NYC

"Three Bronx Bombers @arod @thejudge44 @yankees #allstarsonly," J.Lo captioned a snap of the two with Yankees player Aaron Judge.

Three Bronx Bombers @arod @thejudge44 @yankees #allstarsonly A post shared by Jennifer Lopez (@jlo) on Jul 7, 2017 at 12:50pm PDT

It seems A-Rod was in town to interview Judge as part of his new gig at Fox Sports.

Me and the Judge... watch my interview w @thejudge44 Tuesday at 730pm on @foxsports #AllStarGame #Allstarsonly A post shared by Alex Rodriguez (@arod) on Jul 7, 2017 at 12:44pm PDT

WATCH: Jennifer Lopez and Alex Rodriguez Show Major PDA in NYC

The cute couple have been inseparable throughout their time in NYC. See their Fourth of July celebrations in the video below.
